                <h1>How to Change Your Wix Page Background Easily</h1>
                <p>Changing the background of a page in Wix is simple and enhances your website's visual appeal. Start by selecting the page you want to modify, then click on 'Change Background' in the settings. You can choose from colors, images, or videos. Make sure your background complements your content for a cohesive design.</p>
